channel.title: Bumper stickers
channel.description:
Here is a list of some funny bumper stickers...
1. Everyone sucks at driving but me 2. There are three kinds of people in this world: those who can count and those who can't. 3. Everyone is entitled to my opinion. 4. Clones are people two. 5. Weather is here, wish you are beautiful. 6. Jesus loves you. Everyone else thinks your a jerk. 7. Honk if ypu want to see my finger 8. honk if your horns broken. 9. If your psychic think honk 10. Honk if you've never seen an UZI coming out of a car window 11. 4 out of 5 of the voices in my head say to kill. The other one tells me to change my socks. 12. YOUR JUST JEALOUs THE VOICES ONLY TALK TO ME! 13. So many cats...so few recipes. 14. Cats aren't clean, they're just covered in cat spit! 15. It is as bad as you think and they are out to get you. 16. I don't suffer from insanity! I enjoy every minute of it!
And my personal favorite... "I support George Bush" Hilarious, isn't it?
I hope you enjoyed my favorite bumper stickers. Feel free to post your favorites.

item.description:

I got some from my local shop, I went with my girlfriend the other day and with my mate also.

  1. If you don’t like my driving, get off the sidewalk
  2. Looking for your cat? Check under my tyres.
  3. I’m horny on all days ending in Y.
  4. Ditch the bitch, lets go fishing.
  5. Curiosity didn’t kill the cat, MY CAR DID

(Here’s one I thought of when I was typing)
Women drivers; No survivors

I can’t remember more so if I do I’ll post em.
